::: {.notes}
- The first missed opportunity are Scientists

- In an analysis we are preparing a journal publication, we looked at the data availability statements in 924 articles published in the Journal of Water, Sanitation and Hygiene for Development from 2011 to 2023.

- A policy for data availability statements was introduced in 2020, after which a remaining 15 % of articles did not include a data availability statement and 60 % of articles stated that data was available in paper.
:::

